{"tid":131531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外資出走中國，波及 4,500 萬人就業","createTime":"2017-02-23T06:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T17:23:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6274c4abec3e25fbbcd0f4e11b10da7c9919234","tid":131531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/20130807/15612616643_835dbfb303_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F20130807%2F15612616643_835dbfb303_z.jpg&h=1c588b03&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國媒體今天報導，中國 2016 年以美元計實際利用外資出現罕見的下降。由於全部外商吸納中國直接就業人數 4,500 萬，應警惕外資撤離伴隨的裁員與失業。 <br />\n<br />\n麵包財經分析，根據官方估算，中國全部外商投資企業吸納的直接就業人數超過 4,500 萬，外資撤離伴隨的裁員與失業值得警惕。外資的不斷撤出，將影響這一龐大就業人群的生計。 <br />\n<br />\n據中國商務部數據，2017 年 1 月中國實際使用外資為 120 億美元，年減 14.73%。 <br />\n<br />\n文章分析，2016 年全年，中國實際利用外資額就已出現罕見下跌。2016 年中國實際利用外資額為 1,260 億美元，與上年相比減少約 2 億美元。即便扣除匯率影響，實際利用外資的增幅也在明顯放緩。 <br />\n<br />\n分析說，更值得關注的是，外商在固定資產投資方面的暴跌。據中國國家統計局數據，2016 年外資在中國固定資產的投資額僅為人民幣 1,211.97 億元。而在 2011 年，這一數字還高達 3,269.81 億元，5 年時間下跌了 62.94%。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2017/02/23/foreign-tradesman-leave-china-affect-4500-million-peoples-work/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2Fforeign-tradesman-leave-china-affect-4500-million-peoples-work%2F&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=35dfb429\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2017/02/23/foreign-tradesman-leave-china-affect-4500-million-peoples-work/</a>"},{"pid":"338e2c6bac5cb674cfb215441831d3a57c9ac866","tid":131531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d75505fcdbc700978c79a3061f4c66ba57d19e9","tid":131531,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499169e8d45359aaddbb40806e2bc1677bd921b4","tid":131531,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7941dab4ca8dd1f3ac5966b235868d508806cf4e","tid":131531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447ed3ab275093f3dd87a8268a26843ebd123a46","tid":131531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a403f423f3a8298cff10ec4d028211db0d6d90","tid":131531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}